# rosetta-frida pre-push hook — the SLOW half.
#
# Runs the full test suite + 100% coverage gate. Combined with the
# pre-commit hook (typecheck + lint + format:check), this matches what
# CI runs end-to-end. Catches coverage regressions before they reach
# GitHub.
#
# Bypass with `git push --no-verify` if you need to push WIP and trust
# CI to catch issues. Discouraged on the master branch.
npm run test:coverage
